{
  "text": "We are now ready to prove the main theorem of this section. (iii) \u21d4 (iv) is proved in a similar fashion to that of (i) \u21d4 (iv) because the condition for being semisimple is left-right symmetric for semiprime rings, so in particular for L K (E) by [CITATION_1] Proposition 3.4] . work has also been supported by the Spanish Ministry of Education and Science under project \"Ingenio Mathematica (i-math)\" No. CSD2006-00032 (Consolider-Ingenio 2010).",
